<!doctype html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
	<style type='text/css'>
		html, body {
			font-family: Arial;
		}
		table, th, tr, td {
			border-collapse: collapse;
		}
		th {
			font-weight: bold;
			text-align: left;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center">
		<tr>
			<td width="100%" valign="top" bgcolor="$parkingOperatorSettingsMap['SECONDARY_COLOR_CODE']" style="padding-top:10px">
				<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" style="border-bottom: 6px solid $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['SECONDARY_COLOR_CODE']; border-top: 1px solid $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['SECONDARY_COLOR_CODE'];">
					<tr>
						<td valign="top" style="padding:0">
							<img src="$parkingOperatorSettingsMap['OPERATOR_LOGO']" style="display: block; padding: 5px; width:200px; height:40px;" />
						</td>
						<td style="padding-right: 30px" align="right" valign="middle">
							<a style="text-decoration: underline; color: $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['PRIMARY_COLOR_CODE'];" href="$parkingOperatorSettingsMap['OPERATOR_WEBSITE']">$parkingOperatorSettingsMap['OPERATOR_WEBSITE_NAME']</a>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" style="padding-top: 10px; color: $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['PRIMARY_COLOR_CODE']">
				<p style="font-weight: bold;">Dear $userVO.fullname,</p>
				<p style="text-align: center;">YOU NOW HAVE ACCESS TO YOUR VERY OWN, CUSTOMISED, PARKING SERVICES PORTAL.</p>
				<p>Welcome to $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['OPERATOR_NAME'], $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['OPERATOR_CATCH_PHRASE']. 
				   We are extremely excited to have you on board and look forward to providing you with efficient parking services via our online portal.</p>				
				<p>Through this Portal, you will have the ability to book parking bays for your visitors online, monitor and manage booking reservations, 
				   and extract reports on the usage of the parking bays over time. 
				   You will be able to do this from your office, home (or even the beach!) using an Internet enabled computer, tablet or smartphone.</p>
				<p>You are already registered to use the portal, simply click on the link below to set your password and log into the portal.</p>
				<br><br>       	  
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" align="center" bgcolor="$parkingOperatorSettingsMap['SECONDARY_COLOR_CODE']" style="color: $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['PRIMARY_COLOR_CODE']; padding:10px 30px 10px 30px;font-size: larger">
				<p>YOUR LOGIN DETAILS</p>
				<p>Username: $userVO.username</span></p> 
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" align="center" style="color: #FFFFFF; padding:10px 30px 10px 30px;font-size: larger"></td>
		</tr>		
		<tr>
			<td align='center' style="padding-top: 20px">
				<table>
					<tr>
						<td valign="top" style="vertical-align: top; padding:10px 30px 10px 30px;" bgcolor="$parkingOperatorSettingsMap['TERTIARY_COLOR_CODE']" align="center">
							<a style="color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:none;font-size: 18px" href='$baseURL/public/user-password-reset-view.xhtml?resetPin=$userPasswordResetVO.resetPin'>Click here to set your password.</a>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding-top:40px">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-bottom: 1px solid $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['SECONDARY_COLOR_CODE']; border-top: 6px solid $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['SECONDARY_COLOR_CODE'];">					
					<tr>            
						<td valign="top" align="center">							
							<p style="color: $parkingOperatorSettingsMap['PRIMARY_COLOR_CODE']; margin: 2px;"><b>$parkingOperatorSettingsMap['OPERATOR_NAME']</b> &copy; 2016, All Rights Reserved.</p>							
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
    </table>	
</body>
</html>